  <p>
    <strong>Vigen</strong> founded PatientBillGuide to make US medical billing more
    understandable for everyday patients. The site combines public CMS data, original
    educational content, and client-side tools — built as an independent project separate
    from any healthcare provider or insurer.
  </p>

  <h2>Focus areas</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Medicare fee schedule benchmarks and fair price heuristics</li>
    <li>Plain-English explanations of CPT codes and billing patterns</li>
    <li>Tool design for uninsured and insured audiences</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Editorial approach</h2>
  <p>
    Content is written for clarity, not to sensationalize billing problems. When evidence is
    limited, we say so. We document methodology, corrections, and limitations openly.
  </p>

